      "body": "Supporting strings with units seems like a good idea, and a good way to clean up inconsistencies like this without losing backwards compatibility.\r\n\r\nBut adding a configuration option to set a \"default unit\" sounds dangerous, because it could cause a script or external piece of software that works well with one node to do something horribly wrong when pointed at a different node, when nodes have different defaults set.",
